  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\n\n```\nCREATE TABLE `table` (`name` VARCHAR(45) NOT NULL);\ninsert into `table` (name) values ('1 1 1'),('2 2 2'),('3 3 3');\nSELECT regexp_replace(name, \"^([[:alnum:]]+)[[:space:]].*$\",\"$1\") FROM `table`;\nSELECT regexp_replace(name, '^([a-zA-Z0-9]+)\\\\s.*$', '$1') FROM `table`;\n\n```\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\nresults from mysql\n```\nMySQL [testdb_1746708950636]> SELECT regexp_replace(name, \"^([[:alnum:]]+)[[:space:]].*$\",\"$1\") FROM `table`;\n+------------------------------------------------------------+\n| regexp_replace(name, \"^([[:alnum:]]+)[[:space:]].*$\",\"$1\") |\n+------------------------------------------------------------+\n| 1                                                          |\n| 2                                                          |\n| 3                                                          |\n+------------------------------------------------------------+\n3 rows in set (0.04 sec)\n```\n\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\nresutls from tidb\n```\nMySQL [testdb_1746708950636]> SELECT regexp_replace(name, \"^([[:alnum:]]+)[[:space:]].*$\",\"$1\") FROM `table`;\n+------------------------------------------------------------+\n| regexp_replace(name, \"^([[:alnum:]]+)[[:space:]].*$\",\"$1\") |\n+------------------------------------------------------------+\n| $1                                                         |\n| $1                                                         |\n| $1                                                         |\n+------------------------------------------------------------+\n3 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n\nMySQL [testdb_1746708950636]> SELECT regexp_replace(name, '^([a-zA-Z0-9]+)\\\\s.*$', '$1') FROM `table`;\n+-----------------------------------------------------+\n| regexp_replace(name, '^([a-zA-Z0-9]+)\\\\s.*$', '$1') |\